What This Dashboard Shows

Panels include:

1️⃣ SSH Brute Force Monitoring

SSH Failed Login Attempts

2️⃣ Network Traffic Monitoring

Detect traffic spikes / scanning

3️⃣ Security Alert Counter

Active alerts in detection engine

4️⃣ Authentication Failures

Live log query from Loki

5️⃣ CPU Usage

Detect resource abuse / crypto mining

6️⃣ Recent Security Events Table

Real-time log feed
How to Import the Dashboard

In Grafana:

Dashboards → Import → Upload JSON

Select:

grafana_dashboard.json

Then choose your datasource:

Prometheus
Loki
